      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>bacon lardons</strong> and cook for 6-7 min or until golden and crispy</p><p>Once crispy, transfer the<strong> bacon</strong> to a plate and reserve the pan and oil for later</p>",
