    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock </strong>to the pan a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all of the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>easy mushroom risotto</strong></p>",
