    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the risotto is cooking, chop your <strong>parsley </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Once done, stir <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) through the mushroom risotto and season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of water if the risotto is looking a little dry!</p>",
