    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>easy mushroom risotto</strong> with the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>bacon</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and <strong>chopped parsley</strong> over the top</p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
